#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "आमुख"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is \"&kwave;\", a simple sound editor built on the &kde-frameworks;. "
"Its features include:"
msgstr ""
"इदं \"&kwave;\" अस्ति, &kde-frameworks; इत्यत्र निर्मितं सरलं ध्वनिसम्पादकं । अस्य "
"विशेषताः सन्ति-"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "a user interface that can be switched to SDI, MDI or Tab mode"
msgstr "एकं उपयोक्तृ-अन्तरफलकं यत् SDI, MDI अथवा Tab मोड् इत्यत्र स्विच् कर्तुं शक्यते"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "simple cut, copy and paste functions"
msgstr "सरलं कट, प्रतिलिपि च पेस्ट् कार्याणि"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "multi-level undo/redo"
msgstr "बहुस्तरीय पूर्ववत/पुनः कर"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "labeling of signals"
msgstr "संकेतानां लेबलिंग्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recording functionality, including pre-recording"
msgstr "पूर्व-रिकार्डिंग् सहितं रिकार्डिङ्ग् कार्यक्षमता"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playback via ALSA, PulseAudio, Qt, and OSS"
msgstr "ALSA, PulseAudio, Qt, OSS इत्येतयोः माध्यमेन प्लेबैक् करणीयम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recording via ALSA, PulseAudio, Qt, and OSS"
msgstr "ALSA, PulseAudio, Qt, OSS इत्येतयोः माध्यमेन रिकार्डिङ्ग्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid "MP3 import/export"
msgstr "MP3 आयात/निर्यात"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ogg/Vorbis and Opus import/export"
msgstr "Ogg/Vorbis तथा Opus आयात/निर्यात"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid "FLAC import/export"
msgstr "FLAC आयात/निर्यात"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid "some analysis functions such as Sonagram"
msgstr "सोनाग्राम इत्यादीनि केचन विश्लेषणकार्याणि"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid "internally uses 24 bit fixed precision for sample data"
msgstr "आन्तरिकरूपेण नमूनादत्तांशस्य कृते २४ बिट् नियतसटीकतायाः उपयोगं करोति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid "free selectable sample rates"
msgstr "निःशुल्क चयनीय नमूना दर"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:395
#, no-c-format
msgid "support for editing of multi channel files"
msgstr "बहुचैनलसञ्चिकानां सम्पादनार्थं समर्थनम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"playback of multi channel audio files (audio output will be mixed down to "
"mono or stereo if needed)"
msgstr ""
"बहुचैनलस्य श्रव्यसञ्चिकानां प्लेबैक (आवश्यकतानुसारं श्रव्यनिर्गमः मोनो अथवा स्टीरियो यावत् "
"मिश्रितः भविष्यति)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid "extendible through an easy-to-use plugin interface"
msgstr "सुलभ-उपयोग-प्लगिन्-अन्तरफलकस्य माध्यमेन विस्तारणीयः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"import/export of other audio formats through <ulink url=\"&url_libaudiofile;"
"\">audiofile</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"&url_libaudiofile;\">audiofile</ulink> इत्यस्य माध्यमेन अन्यस्य "
"श्रव्यस्वरूपस्य आयातः/निर्यातः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:412
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are interested what has been done and what has still to be done, then "
"look at the files <filename>CHANGES</filename> and <filename>TODO</filename> "
"included in the source package. Help and constructive critics are always "
"welcome."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् किं कृतं किं च कर्तव्यं इति रुचिं लभते तर्हि स्रोतसङ्कुलमध्ये समाविष्टानि "
"<filename>CHANGES</filename> <filename>TODO</filename> च सञ्चिकाः पश्यन्तु । "
"सहायतां रचनात्मकं च समीक्षकाणां सदैव स्वागतं भवति।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:424
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kwave; Resources"
msgstr "& अभवत्; संसाधनाः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"So if you want to get in contact with the developers, need some further help "
"on using &kwave;, submit patches, bug reports or other stuff, the following "
