#: index.docbook:6460 index.docbook:6685 index.docbook:6799 index.docbook:6810
#: index.docbook:6948 index.docbook:7002
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot"
msgstr "स्क्रीनशॉट"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2786
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the label editing dialog"
msgstr "लेबल सम्पादनसंवादस्य स्क्रीनशॉट्"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2791
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_label_edit;</"
"command>(<replaceable>index</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-cmd_label_edit;</"
"command>(<प्रतिस्थापनीय>अनुक्रमणिका</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2792
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a dialog window in which the user can edit the position and the "
"description of a label, which is identified by its index (starting from "
"zero). If no label with the given index exists, this command does nothing."
msgstr ""
"एकं संवादविण्डो उद्घाटयति यस्मिन् उपयोक्ता लेबलस्य स्थानं वर्णनं च सम्पादयितुं शक्नोति, यत् "
"तस्य अनुक्रमणिकाद्वारा (शून्यतः आरभ्य) चिह्नितं भवति । यदि दत्तसूचकाङ्कयुक्तं लेबलं नास्ति "
"तर्हि एषः आदेशः किमपि न करोति ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2800
#, no-c-format
msgid "index of the label to edit, starting with 0"
msgstr "सम्पादनार्थं लेबलस्य अनुक्रमणिका, 0 इत्यस्मात् आरभ्य"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2805
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_loadbatch;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_loadbatch;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2807
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_loadbatch;</"
"command>(<replaceable>filename</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-cmd_loadbatch;</"
"command>(<प्रतिस्थापनीय>सञ्चिकानाम</प्रतिस्थापनीय>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2808
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a &kwave; script file and processes the commands in it. Uses the "
"context of the currently opened file or the current main window if no file "
"is loaded."
msgstr ""
"एकं &kwave उद्घाटयति; script file इति कृत्वा तस्मिन् आदेशान् संसाधयति । वर्तमानं "
"उद्घाटितायाः सञ्चिकायाः अथवा वर्तमानस्य मुख्यविण्डो इत्यस्य सन्दर्भं उपयुङ्क्ते यदि कोऽपि "
"सञ्चिका लोड् न भवति ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2815 index.docbook:3138 index.docbook:3164 index.docbook:3460
#: index.docbook:3493 index.docbook:4234
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>filename</parameter>:"
msgstr "<parameter>सञ्चिकानाम</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2816
#, no-c-format
msgid "name of the kwave script file including path and extension"
msgstr "मार्गः विस्तारश्च सहितं kwave स्क्रिप्ट् सञ्चिकायाः नाम"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2821
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_loop;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_लूप;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2823
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_loop;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_loop;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2824
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the <guibutton>Loop</guibutton> toolbar button. Starts the "
"playback (if it is not already running) and lets it play in a loop."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Loop</guibutton> साधनपट्टिकाबटनस्य अनुरूपम् अस्ति । प्लेबैक् आरभते (यदि "
"पूर्वमेव न प्रचलति) तथा च लूप् मध्ये प्ले कर्तुं ददाति ।"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:2832
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_playback_start;</command>()"
msgstr "<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_playback_start;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2838
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;m"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;m"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2841
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_menu;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_menu;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2843
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_menu;</command> "
"(<replaceable>command</replaceable>, <replaceable>path</replaceable>, "
"[<replaceable>hotkey</replaceable>], [<replaceable>id</replaceable>])"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_menu;</command> (<प्रतिस्थापनीय>आदेशः</"
"replaceable>, <replaceable>मार्गः</replaceable>, [<replaceable>hotkey</"
"replaceable>], [<replaceable >इद्</replaceable>]) इति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2849
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a very powerful command, which is used to add a new entry to the "
"menu or to modify an existing entry. It determines which <emphasis>command</"
"emphasis> is executed when the menu entry is activated, which "
"<emphasis>icon</emphasis> is shown in the menu and which <emphasis>hotkey</"
"emphasis> is used. Each menu entry can be <emphasis>disabled</emphasis> or "
"<emphasis>hidden</emphasis>, can be assigned a unique <emphasis>id</"
"emphasis> and can also join a <emphasis>menu group</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"एषः अतीव शक्तिशाली आदेशः अस्ति, यस्य उपयोगः मेन्यू मध्ये नूतनं प्रविष्टिं योजयितुं वा "
"विद्यमानं प्रविष्टिं परिवर्तयितुं वा भवति । मेनूप्रविष्टिः सक्रियतायां कः <emphasis>आदेशः</"
"emphasis> निष्पादितः भवति, मेनूमध्ये कः <emphasis>चिह्न</emphasis> दर्शितः, कः "
"<emphasis>hotkey</emphasis> उपयुज्यते इति निर्धारयति प्रत्येकं मेनूप्रविष्टिः "
"<emphasis>अक्षम</emphasis> अथवा <emphasis>hidden</emphasis> भवितुम् अर्हति, "
"अद्वितीयं <emphasis>id</emphasis> नियुक्तं कर्तुं शक्यते तथा च <emphasis>मेनूसमूहे</"
"emphasis> अपि सम्मिलितुं शक्यते ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2860
#, no-c-format
msgid "You normally do not need this command within a &kwave; script!"
msgstr "सामान्यतया भवतः &kwave; प्रलेखन!"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2867
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A text command (including parameters) or a command list that will be "
"executed when the menu entry gets activated. If a menu entry does not have a "
"corresponding command (for example if it is a sub menu and not menu entry), "
"you should use the special command <command>ignore</command>()."
msgstr ""
"पाठनिर्देशः (पैरामीटर्स् सहितम्) अथवा आदेशसूची या मेनूप्रविष्टिः सक्रियताम् अवाप्नोति तदा "
"निष्पादिता भविष्यति । यदि मेन्यू-प्रविष्टेः तत्सम्बद्धः आदेशः नास्ति (उदाहरणार्थं यदि उपमेनू "
"अस्ति न तु मेन्यू-प्रविष्टिः), तर्हि भवान् <command>ignore</command>() इति विशेष-आदेशस्य "
"उपयोगं कर्तव्यः ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2876
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>path</parameter>:"
msgstr "<पैरामीटर्>मार्गः</parameter>: ."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2877
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The path within the menu, using a <quote><token>/</token></quote> as "
"separator. The last part of the path can be a <emphasis>sub command</"
"emphasis> which modifies some property of the menu entry (see <link linkend="
"\"menu_sub_commands\">below</link>). The last portion of the path (that is "
"not a sub command) produces a menu entry, the parts before produce the main "
"menu entry or sub menus that lead to it. Main menu entries or sub menus are "
"automatically created when a menu entry is created, you do not need them "
"manually."
msgstr ""
"मेनूमध्ये मार्गः, क इत्यस्य उपयोगेन<quote><token> / .</token></quote> विभाजकत्वेन । "
"मार्गस्य अन्तिमः भागः क<emphasis> उप आदेशः</emphasis> यत् मेनूप्रविष्टेः किञ्चित् गुणं "
"परिवर्तयति (द्रष्टव्यम्<link linkend=\"menu_sub_commands\"> अधः</link> ). मार्गस्य "
"अन्तिमः भागः (यः उप-आदेशः नास्ति) मेनू-प्रविष्टिं उत्पादयति, पूर्वभागाः मुख्यमेनू-प्रविष्टिं "
"वा उपमेनू-उत्पादयन्ति ये तत् प्रति गच्छन्ति । मुख्यमेनूप्रविष्टयः उपमेनूः वा स्वयमेव निर्मीयन्ते "
"यदा मेनूप्रविष्टिः निर्मीयते, भवतः स्वहस्तेन आवश्यकता नास्ति ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2890
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>hotkey</parameter>:"
msgstr "<पैरामीटर्>हॉटकी</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2891
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A bitmask that consists of a combination of predefined <emphasis>keys</"
"emphasis> and <emphasis>modifiers</emphasis>, concatenated with a "
"<quote><token>+</token></quote>. The <emphasis>key</emphasis> can be either "
"a digit, an upper case letter, a function key (<quote>F1</quote> ... "
"<quote>F12</quote>) or any other key name understood by the Qt class "
"<quote><literal>QKeySequence</literal></quote>, including key names for "
"predefined actions (like for example <quote><literal>::Copy</literal></"
"quote>). Typical <emphasis>modifiers</emphasis> are <quote><literal>SHIFT</"
"literal></quote>, <quote><literal>ALT</literal></quote> and "
"<quote><literal>CTRL</literal></quote>."
msgstr ""
"पूर्वनिर्धारित <emphasis>कील</emphasis> तथा <emphasis>संशोधक</emphasis> इत्येतयोः "
"संयोजनेन युक्तं बिटमास्कं, <quote><token>+</token></quote> इत्यनेन सह सम्बद्धम् "
"<emphasis>key</emphasis> अङ्कः, बृहत् अक्षरः, फंक्शन् कीलः (<quote>F1</quote> ... "
"<quote>F12</quote>) अथवा अन्यत् किमपि कीलनाम अवगतं वा भवितुम् अर्हति Qt वर्गेन "
"<quote><literal>QKeySequence</literal></quote> द्वारा, पूर्वनिर्धारितक्रियाणां कृते "
"कुञ्जीनामानि समाविष्टानि (यथा उदाहरणार्थम् <quote><literal>::प्रतिलिपि</literal></"
"quote>)। विशिष्टाः <emphasis>संशोधकाः</emphasis> <quote><literal>SHIFT</"
"literal></quote>, <quote><literal>ALT</literal></quote> तथा "
"<quote><literal>CTRL< च सन्ति /शाब्दिक></उद्धरण>।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2909
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>id</parameter>:"
msgstr "<पैरामीटर्>इड</पैरामीटर>: ."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2910
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A unique id that can be internally used to identify this menu entry or "
"menu / sub menu. Only uppercase letters, digits and <quote><literal>_</"
"literal></quote> should be used and it should start with "
"<quote><literal>ID_</literal></quote>. It is in your own responsibility to "
"make sure that the same id is not used twice."
msgstr ""
"एकं अद्वितीयं id यस्य उपयोगः आन्तरिकरूपेण अस्य मेनूप्रविष्टेः अथवा मेनू / उपमेनूस्य परिचयार्थं "
"कर्तुं शक्यते । केवलं बृहत् अक्षराणि, अङ्काः, <quote><literal>_</literal></quote> च "
"प्रयोक्तव्याः तथा च <quote><literal>ID_</literal></quote> इत्यनेन आरभ्यत । एकस्यैव "
"id इत्यस्य द्विवारं उपयोगः न भवति इति सुनिश्चितं कर्तुं भवतः स्वस्य दायित्वम् अस्ति।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2920
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sub Commands"
msgstr "उप आदेश"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2922
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;#checkable</command>:"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;#परीक्षणीय</command>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2923
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Makes the menu entry <emphasis>checkable</emphasis>, so that it can be "
"switched on or off."
msgstr ""
"मेनू-प्रविष्टिं <emphasis>checkable</emphasis> करोति, येन तत् चालू अथवा निष्क्रियं कर्तुं "
"शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2928
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;#disabled</command>:"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;#अक्षम</command>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2929
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Disables</emphasis> the menu, sub menu or menu entry."
msgstr "<emphasis>मेनू, उपमेनू अथवा मेनूप्रविष्टिं निष्क्रियं करोति</emphasis> ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2933
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;#enabled</command>:"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;#सक्षम</command>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2934
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Enables</emphasis> the menu, sub menu or menu entry."
msgstr "<emphasis>मेनू, उपमेनू अथवा मेनूप्रविष्टिं सक्षमं करोति</emphasis> ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2938
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>#exclusive</command>(<replaceable>group</replaceable>):"
msgstr "<command>#exclusive</command>(<प्रतिस्थापनीय>समूह</प्रतिस्थापनीय>): ."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2939
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adds the menu entry to an <emphasis>exclusive</emphasis> "
"<emphasis><replaceable>group</replaceable></emphasis> (one of many "
"selection). The group that is given as parameter should not be used for any "
"other purpose. Only one entry within that group can be selected at a time."
msgstr ""
"मेनूप्रविष्टिं <emphasis>exclusive</emphasis> <emphasis><replaceable>समूहे</"
"replaceable></emphasis> (बहुषु चयनेषु अन्यतमम्) इत्यत्र योजयति । यः समूहः पैरामीटर् इति "
"दत्तः सः अन्यस्य प्रयोजनार्थं न प्रयोक्तव्यः । तस्मिन् समूहे एकैकं प्रविष्टिः एव एकस्मिन् समये "
"चयनं कर्तुं शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2947
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>#group</command>(<replaceable>list</replaceable>):"
msgstr "<command>#group</command>(<प्रतिस्थापनीय>सूची</प्रतिस्थापनीय>):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2948
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adds the menu, sub menu or menu entry to one or more a <emphasis>groups</"
"emphasis>, so that the application can enable/disable a bunch of menu "
"entries without need to know all their unique ids. Multiple groups can be "
"passed as a list with a <quote><literal>,</literal></quote> as separator. "
"Group names have to start with a <quote><literal>@</literal></quote>. The "
"following groups are predefined:"
msgstr ""
"मेनू, उपमेनू अथवा मेनू प्रविष्टिं एकस्मिन् वा अधिके <emphasis>groups</emphasis> मध्ये "
"योजयति, येन अनुप्रयोगः मेनूप्रविष्टीनां समूहं सक्षम/अक्षमं कर्तुं शक्नोति यत्र तेषां सर्वाणि "
"अद्वितीय-ids ज्ञातुं आवश्यकता नास्ति बहुसमूहाः <quote><literal>,</literal></quote> "
"इत्यनेन सह सूचीरूपेण विभाजकरूपेण पारयितुं शक्यन्ते । समूहनामानां आरम्भः <quote><literal>@</"
"literal></quote> इत्यनेन करणीयम् । निम्नलिखितसमूहाः पूर्वनिर्धारिताः सन्ति ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2959
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;@CLIPBOARD</command>:"
msgstr "<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;@CLIPBOARD</command>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2961
#, no-c-format
msgid "Only enabled when the clipboard is not empty."
msgstr "केवलं तदा सक्षमम् यदा क्लिप्बोर्ड् रिक्तं न भवति ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2967
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;@LABELS</command>:"
msgstr "<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;@LABELS</command>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2969
#, no-c-format
msgid "Only enabled when the current signal contains at least one label."
msgstr "केवलं तदा सक्षमः यदा वर्तमानसंकेते न्यूनातिन्यूनम् एकं लेबलं भवति ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2976
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;@NOT_CLOSED</command>:"
msgstr "<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;@NOT_CLOSED</command>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2978
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enabled when the current signal is not closed (the signal might be empty or "
"zero length)."
msgstr ""
"यदा वर्तमानसंकेतः न निमीलितः भवति तदा सक्षमः भवति (संकेतः रिक्तः शून्यदीर्घता वा भवितुम् "
"अर्हति) ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2985
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;@SELECTION</command>:"
msgstr "<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;@चयन</command>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2987
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enabled when the selection is not empty (more than one sample is selected)."
msgstr "यदा चयनं रिक्तं नास्ति (एकस्मात् अधिकं नमूनानि चयनितम्) तदा सक्षमम् ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2994
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;@SIGNAL</command>:"
msgstr "<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;@SIGNAL</command>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2996
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enabled when there is some signal loaded and it is not empty or zero length."
msgstr ""
"यदा कश्चन संकेतः भारितः भवति तथा च सः रिक्तः शून्यदीर्घता वा नास्ति तदा सक्षमम् ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3005
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;#hidden</command>:"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;#गुप्त</command>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3006
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Hides</emphasis> the menu, sub menu or menu entry."
msgstr "<emphasis>मेनू, उपमेनू अथवा मेनूप्रविष्टिं गोपयति</emphasis> ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3009
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>#icon</command>(<replaceable>name</replaceable>):"
msgstr "<command>#icon</command>(<प्रतिस्थापनीय>नाम</प्रतिस्थापनीय>): ."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3010
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Assigns an <emphasis>icon</emphasis> to the menu entry. The icon "
"<emphasis><replaceable>name</replaceable></emphasis> should correspond to an "
"icon file (without path and file extension) that is installed on the system "
"or with &kwave;."
msgstr ""
"मेनूप्रविष्टौ <emphasis>चिह्न</emphasis> नियुङ्क्ते । <emphasis><replaceable>name</"
"replaceable></emphasis> इति चिह्नं प्रणाल्यां अथवा &kwave; इत्यनेन सह संस्थापितायाः "
"चिह्नसञ्चिकायाः (मार्गस्य सञ्चिकाविस्तारस्य च विना) अनुरूपं भवेत् ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3018
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>#listmenu</command>(<replaceable>id</replaceable>,"
"<replaceable>command</replaceable>):"
msgstr ""
"<command>#listmenu</command>(<प्रतिस्थापनीय>id</replaceable>,<प्रतिस्थापनीय>आदेश</"
"replaceable>):"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3019
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserts a placeholder for a list of menu entries into a sub menu. The unique "
"<emphasis><replaceable>id</replaceable></emphasis> specified in this sub "
"command is used to add/remove or clear the list of menu entries. The "
"<emphasis><replaceable>command</replaceable></emphasis> parameter has to "
"contain <quote><literal>%1</literal></quote> as parameter, which will be "
"replaced with the text of the menu entry when it is activated. This sub "
"command is internally used for the list of recent files, list of tracks and "
"window list."
msgstr ""
"उपमेनूमध्ये मेनूप्रविष्टीनां सूचीयाः कृते स्थानधारकं निवेशयति । अस्मिन् उप-आदेशे निर्दिष्टं "
"अद्वितीयं <emphasis><replaceable>id</replaceable></emphasis> मेनू-प्रविष्टीनां सूचीं "
"योजयितुं/निष्कासयितुं वा स्वच्छं कर्तुं वा उपयुज्यते । <emphasis><replaceable>आदेश</"
"replaceable></emphasis> पैरामीटर् मध्ये <quote><literal>%1</literal></quote> "
"पैरामीटर् रूपेण भवितव्यम्, यत् मेनू प्रविष्टेः पाठेन प्रतिस्थापितं भविष्यति यदा सक्रियः भवति। "
"एषः उप-आदेशः आन्तरिकरूपेण अद्यतनसञ्चिकानां सूची, पटलानां सूची, विण्डो सूची च कृते उपयुज्यते ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3033
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;#separator</command>:"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;#विभाजक</command>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3034
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inserts a separator into a sub menu."
msgstr "उपमेनूमध्ये विभाजकं निवेशयति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3044
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_msgbox;"
msgstr "& no-i18n-cmd_msgbox;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3046
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_msgbox;</command>(<replaceable>text</"
"replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-cmd_msgbox;</command>(<प्रतिस्थापनीय>पाठ</"
"प्रतिस्थापनीय>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3047
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows a message box with some <emphasis><replaceable>text</replaceable></"
"emphasis> and the two buttons <guibutton>OK</guibutton> (returns without "
"error code) and <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> (returns and error code). You "
"can use this command to give the user a possibility to abort a running "
"script."
msgstr ""
"केनचित् <emphasis><replaceable>text</replaceable></emphasis> इत्यनेन सह "
"सन्देशपेटिकां दर्शयति तथा च <guibutton>OK</guibutton> (दोषसङ्केतं विना प्रत्यागच्छति) "
"तथा <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> (प्रत्यागच्छति) इति बटनद्वयं दर्शयति तथा "
"त्रुटिसङ्केतः)। उपयोक्त्रे चालितं स्क्रिप्ट् निरस्तं कर्तुं संभावनां दातुं भवान् एतत् आदेशं उपयोक्तुं "
"शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3056
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A message that will be shown in the message box, should contain a question "
"that can be answered with <guibutton>OK</guibutton> or <guibutton>Cancel</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"सन्देशपेटिकायां दर्शयिष्यमाणः सन्देशः, <guibutton>OK</guibutton> अथवा "
"<guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> इत्यनेन उत्तरं दातुं शक्यते इति प्रश्नः भवितुमर्हति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3066
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;n"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;n"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3069
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_newsignal;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_न्यूसिग्नल;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3071
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_newsignal;</"
"command>( <replaceable>samples</replaceable>, <replaceable>rate</"
"replaceable>, <replaceable>bits</replaceable>, <replaceable>tracks</"
"replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_newsignal;</"
"command>( <प्रतिस्थापनीय>नमूना</replaceable>, <replaceable>दर</replaceable>, "
"<replaceable>बिट्</replaceable>, <replaceable>tracks< /प्रतिस्थापनीय>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3077
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a new signal, with a given length in <emphasis><replaceable>samples</"
"replaceable></emphasis>, a <emphasis><replaceable>rate</replaceable></"
"emphasis> in samples per second (floating point number), a number of "
"<emphasis><replaceable>bits</replaceable></emphasis> per sample and number "
"of <emphasis><replaceable>tracks</replaceable></emphasis>. You can calculate "
"the length in samples by multiplying the desired length in seconds with the "
"sample rate."
msgstr ""
"नूतनं संकेतं निर्माति, यत्र <emphasis><replaceable>samples</replaceable></emphasis> "
"इत्यत्र दत्तदीर्घता, प्रति सेकण्ड् नमूनासु <emphasis><replaceable>दर</replaceable></"
"emphasis> (प्लवमानबिन्दुसङ्ख्या) भवति ), प्रति नमूना <emphasis><replaceable>बिट्</"
"replaceable></emphasis> इत्यस्य संख्या तथा च <emphasis><replaceable>पट्टिकाः</"
"replaceable></emphasis> इति । नमूनादरेण सह इष्टदीर्घतां सेकण्डेषु गुणयित्वा नमूनासु "
"दीर्घतां गणयितुं शक्नुवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3089
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>samples</parameter>:"
msgstr "<पैरामीटर्>नमूना</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3090
#, no-c-format
msgid "Length of the signal in samples."
msgstr "नमूनासु संकेतस्य दीर्घता ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3091
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>rate</parameter>:"
msgstr "<पैरामीटर्>दर</parameter>: ."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3092
#, no-c-format
msgid "<entry>Sample rate in samples per second.</entry>"
msgstr "<entry>प्रति सेकण्ड् नमूनासु नमूनादरः।</entry>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3093
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>bits</parameter>:"
msgstr "<पैरामीटर्>बिट्स्</parameter>: ."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3094
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Number of bits per sample, must not be zero, should be a number from 8...32."
msgstr "प्रतिनमूना बिट्-सङ्ख्या, शून्यं न भवितुमर्हति, ८...३२ तः सङ्ख्या भवितुमर्हति ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3096
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>tracks</parameter>:"
msgstr "<पैरामीटर्>पट्टिकाः</parameter>:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3097
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of tracks."
msgstr "पटलानां संख्या ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3102
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_next;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_next;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3104
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_next;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_next;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the <guibutton>Next</guibutton> toolbar button. If the "
"playback is currently running, it skips forward to the next label. If the "
"playback is not running, this does the same as the command <command>&no-i18n-"
"cmd_view_scroll_next_label;</command>()."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Next</guibutton> इति साधनपट्टिकाबटनस्य अनुरूपं भवति । यदि प्लेबैक् सम्प्रति "
"प्रचलति तर्हि अग्रिमलेबलं प्रति अग्रे लङ्घयति । यदि प्लेबैक् न चाल्यते तर्हि एतत् "
"<command>&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_next_label;</command>() इत्यस्य आदेशस्य समानं "
"करोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_view_scroll_next_label\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-"
"i18n-cmd_view_scroll_next_label;</command>()</link>, <link linkend="
"\"cmd_sect_prev\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_prev;</command>()</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_view_scroll_next_label\"><command>&amp;no-i18n-tag;"
"&amp;no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_next_label;</command> () ९.</link> , ९.<link "
"linkend=\"cmd_sect_prev\"><command> &amp;no-i18n-tag;&amp;no-i18n-cmd_prev;</"
"command> () ९.</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3122
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;o"
msgstr "&न-इ१८न-टैग;ओ"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3125
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_open;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_open;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_open;</"
"command>([<replaceable>filename</replaceable>])"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-cmd_open;</command>([<प्रतिस्थापनीय>सञ्चिकानाम</"
"प्रतिस्थापनीय>])"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a file, which can be either a sound file or a &kwave; script. If no "
"file name is passed, then a dialog window will be opened that allows to "
"select an existing file. Depending on the &GUI; mode the file will be opened "
"in the context of a new sub-window (MDI and tab) or in a new main window "
"(SDI, if there was already something loaded)."
msgstr ""
"सञ्चिकां उद्घाटयति, या ध्वनिसञ्चिका वा &kwave; प्रलेखन। यदि सञ्चिकानाम न पारितं तर्हि "
"संवादविण्डो उद्घाट्यते यत् विद्यमानसञ्चिकां चयनं कर्तुं शक्नोति । &GUI इत्यस्य आधारेण; mode "
"सञ्चिका नूतनस्य उप-विण्डो (MDI तथा tab) सन्दर्भे अथवा नूतने मुख्यविण्डो (SDI, यदि पूर्वमेव "
"किमपि लोड् आसीत्) सन्दर्भे उद्घाटिता भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3139
#, no-c-format
msgid "name of a file including path and extension"
msgstr "मार्गः विस्तारश्च सहितस्य सञ्चिकायाः नाम"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3143 index.docbook:3332
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_close;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_close;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3149
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_openrecent;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_openrecent;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_openrecent;</"
"command>(<replaceable>filename</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-cmd_openrecent;</"
"command>(<प्रतिस्थापनीय>सञ्चिकानाम</प्रतिस्थापनीय>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Practically the same as the command <command>&no-i18n-cmd_open;</command>(), "
"but intended to be used internally for the list of recently opened files in "
"the menu <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenu>Open Recent</guimenu> "
"</menuchoice>. In this command the parameter <replaceable>filename</"
"replaceable> is not optional."
msgstr ""
"व्यावहारिकरूपेण <command>&no-i18n-cmd_open;</command>() इति आदेशस्य समानं, परन्तु मेनू "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu>< इत्यत्र सद्यः उद्घाटितानां सञ्चिकानां सूचीयाः "
"कृते आन्तरिकरूपेण उपयोक्तुं अभिप्रेतम् guimenu>अद्यतन</guimenu> </menuchoice> उद्घाटयन्तु । "
"अस्मिन् आदेशे <replaceable>filename</replaceable> इति पैरामीटर् वैकल्पिकं नास्ति ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3165
#, no-c-format
msgid "entry of the list of recently opened files"
msgstr "सद्यः उद्घाटितानां सञ्चिकानां सूचीयाः प्रविष्टिः"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3169
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_open;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_open;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3175
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;p"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;p"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3178
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_paste;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_paste;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3180
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_paste;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_paste;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Replaces the current selection with the content of the clipboard. If the "
"clipboard is empty, this command does nothing. The sample rate of the "
"inserted data is adjusted to match the sample rate of the current signal if "
"necessary. Only enabled tracks are affected, disabled tracks remain "
"unchanged. Please be aware that this might produce a time shift between "
"enabled and disabled tracks! If the number of tracks of the clipboard data "
"differs from the number of enabled tracks, then the data is mixed to be "
"spread equally over all selected tracks."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमानचयनस्य स्थाने क्लिप्बोर्डस्य सामग्रीं स्थापयति । यदि क्लिप्बोर्ड् रिक्तं भवति तर्हि एषः "
"आदेशः किमपि न करोति । सम्मिलितदत्तांशस्य नमूनादरः आवश्यके सति वर्तमानसंकेतस्य नमूनादरेण सह "
"मेलयितुम् समायोजितः भवति । केवलं सक्षमाः पटलाः प्रभाविताः भवन्ति, अक्षमाः पटलाः "
"अपरिवर्तिताः एव तिष्ठन्ति । कृपया अवगच्छन्तु यत् एतेन सक्षम-अक्षम-पट्टिकानां मध्ये समय-"
"परिवर्तनं भवितुम् अर्हति! यदि क्लिप्बोर्डदत्तांशस्य पटलसङ्ख्या सक्षमपट्टिकासङ्ख्यातः भिन्ना "
"भवति तर्हि सर्वेषु चयनितपट्टिकासु समानरूपेण प्रसारयितुं दत्तांशः मिश्रितः भवति"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3196
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_copy;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_copy;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3202
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_pause;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_pause;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the <guibutton>Pause</guibutton> toolbar button and lets the "
"playback pause if it is currently running, or continue if it is currently "
"paused."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Pause</guibutton> साधनपट्टिकाबटनस्य अनुरूपं भवति तथा च यदि सम्प्रति "
"प्रचलति तर्हि प्लेबैक् विरामं कर्तुं ददाति, अथवा सम्प्रति विरामितं चेत् निरन्तरं कर्तुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3213
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_continue;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_continue;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3219
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_playback_start;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_प्लेबैक_प्रारम्भ;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_playback_start;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_playback_start;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the <guibutton>Start</guibutton> toolbar button and lets the "
"playback start if it is currently paused."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Start</guibutton> साधनपट्टिकाबटनस्य अनुरूपं भवति तथा च यदि सम्प्रति "
"विरामितम् अस्ति तर्हि प्लेबैक् आरभ्यतुं ददाति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3230
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_plugin;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_प्लगिन्;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_plugin;</command>(<replaceable>name</"
"replaceable>, [<replaceable>parameter</replaceable> ...])"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_plugin;</command>(<प्रतिस्थापनीय>नाम</"
"प्रतिस्थापनीय>, [<प्रतिस्थापनीय>पैरामीटर</प्रतिस्थापनीय> ...])"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Executes a plugin, with an optional list of parameters. If no parameter list "
"is given, then the setup function of the plugin will be called, using the "
"parameters of the previous invocation or default parameters as input "
"(normally shows a setup dialog, depending on the plugin). Please refer to "
"the chapter about <link linkend=\"plugins\">plugins</link> for a description "
"of the various plugins."
msgstr ""
"प्लगिन् निष्पादयति, पैरामीटर्स् इत्यस्य वैकल्पिकसूचया सह । यदि कोऽपि पैरामीटर् सूची न "
"दत्ता, तर्हि प्लगिन् इत्यस्य सेटअप फंक्शन् आह्वयते, पूर्वस्य आह्वानस्य अथवा पूर्वनिर्धारित "
"पैरामीटर् इत्यस्य पैरामीटर्स् इत्यस्य उपयोगेन इनपुट् रूपेण (सामान्यतया सेटअप संवादं दर्शयति, "
"प्लगिन् इत्यस्य आधारेण) कृपया विषये अध्यायं पश्यन्तु<link linkend=\"plugins\"> प्लगिन्स्</"
"link> विभिन्नानां प्लगिन्स् इत्यस्य वर्णनार्थम् ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3244 index.docbook:3268 index.docbook:3290
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>name</parameter>:"
msgstr "<पैरामीटर्>नाम</पैरामीटर्>: ."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3245 index.docbook:3269 index.docbook:3291
#, no-c-format
msgid "the (internal) name of a &kwave; plugin"
msgstr "a (आन्तरिकं) नाम &wave; प्लगिन्"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3246 index.docbook:3270 index.docbook:3292
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>parameter</parameter>:"
msgstr "<पैरामीटर्>पैरामीटर्</parameter>: ."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3247 index.docbook:3293
#, no-c-format
msgid "a list of parameters understood by the plugin (optional)"
msgstr "प्लगिन् द्वारा अवगतानां मापदण्डानां सूची (वैकल्पिकम्)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_plugin_execute\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-"
"cmd_plugin_execute;</command>()</link>, <link linkend=\"cmd_sect_plugin_setup"
"\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_plugin_setup;</command>()</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_plugin_execute\"><command>&amp;कोई-i18n-टैग;&amp;कोई-"
"i18n-cmd_plugin_execute;</command> () ९.</link> , ९.<link linkend="
"\"cmd_sect_plugin_setup\"><command> &amp;no-i18n-टैग;&amp;no-i18n-"
"cmd_plugin_setup;</command> () ९.</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3258
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_plugin_execute;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_प्लगइन_निष्पादन;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_plugin_execute;</"
"command>(<replaceable>name</replaceable>, [<replaceable>parameter</"
"replaceable> ...])"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-cmd_plugin_execute;</"
"command>(<प्रतिस्थापनीय>नाम</प्रतिस्थापनीय>, [<प्रतिस्थापनीय>पैरामीटर</"
"प्रतिस्थापनीय> ...])"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similar to the command <command>&no-i18n-cmd_plugin;</command>(), but "
"without calling the setup function of the plugin if no parameters were "
"passed."
msgstr ""
"<command>&no-i18n-cmd_plugin;</command>() इति आदेशस्य सदृशं, परन्तु यदि कोऽपि "
"पैरामीटर् पारितः नासीत् तर्हि प्लगिन् इत्यस्य सेटअप फंक्शन् आह्वयित्वा विना ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3271
#, no-c-format
msgid "a list of parameters understood by the plugin"
msgstr "प्लगिन् द्वारा अवगतानां मापदण्डानां सूची"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3276
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_plugin_setup;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_प्लगइन_सेटअप;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_plugin_setup;</"
"command>(<replaceable>name</replaceable>, [<replaceable>parameter</"
"replaceable> ...])"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-cmd_plugin_setup;</command>(<प्रतिस्थापनीय>नाम</"
"प्रतिस्थापनीय>, [<प्रतिस्थापनीय>पैरामीटर</प्रतिस्थापनीय> ...])"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Calls the <emphasis>setup</emphasis> function of a plugin, with an optional "
"list of parameters. If no parameter list is given, the parameters of the "
"previous invocation or default parameters will be used as input. This "
"normally shows a setup dialog, depending on the plugin. Please refer to the "
"chapter about <link linkend=\"plugins\">plugins</link> for a description of "
"the various plugins."
msgstr ""
"आह्वयति<emphasis> स्थापयति</emphasis> प्लगिन् इत्यस्य कार्यं, पैरामीटर्स् इत्यस्य "
"वैकल्पिकसूचया सह । यदि कोऽपि पैरामीटर् सूची न दत्ता तर्हि पूर्वस्य आह्वानस्य अथवा "
"पूर्वनिर्धारितपैरामीटर् इत्यस्य पैरामीटर्स् इनपुट् रूपेण उपयुज्यन्ते । एतत् सामान्यतया प्लगिन् "
"इत्यस्य आधारेण सेटअप संवादं दर्शयति । कृपया विषये अध्यायं पश्यन्तु<link linkend=\"plugins"
"\"> प्लगिन्स्</link> विभिन्नानां प्लगिन्स् इत्यस्य वर्णनार्थम् ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3298
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_prev;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_पूर्व;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3300
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_prev;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_prev;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the <guibutton>Previous</guibutton> toolbar button. If the "
"playback is currently running, it skips back to the previous label or start "
"of the selection. If the playback is not running, this does the same as the "
"command <command>&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_prev_label;</command>()."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>पूर्व</guibutton> साधनपट्टिकाबटनस्य अनुरूपं भवति । यदि प्लेबैक् सम्प्रति "
"प्रचलति तर्हि पूर्वलेबल् अथवा चयनस्य आरम्भं प्रति पुनः लङ्घयति । यदि प्लेबैक् न चाल्यते तर्हि "
"एतत् <command>&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_prev_label;</command>() इत्यस्य आदेशस्य "
"समानं करोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_view_scroll_next_label\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-"
"i18n-cmd_view_scroll_prev_label;</command>()</link>, <link linkend="
"\"cmd_sect_next\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_next;</command>()</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_view_scroll_next_label\"><command>&amp;no-i18n-tag;"
"&amp;no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_prev_label;</command> () ९.</link> , ९.<link "
"linkend=\"cmd_sect_next\"><command> &amp;no-i18n-tag;&amp;no-i18n-cmd_next;</"
"command> () ९.</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3318
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;q"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;q"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3321
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_quit;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_quit;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3323
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_quit;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_quit;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Closes the current main window, including all sub-windows. In SDI mode this "
"is the same as the command <command>&no-i18n-cmd_close;</command>()."
msgstr ""
"सर्वाणि उपविण्डोः सहितं वर्तमानं मुख्यविण्डो पिधायति । SDI मोड् मध्ये एतत् <command>&no-"
"i18n-cmd_close;</command>() इत्यस्य आदेशस्य समानम् अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3338
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;r"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;r"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3341
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_redo;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_redo;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3343
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_redo;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_redo;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3344
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the <guibutton>Redo</guibutton> toolbar button and repeats "
"one operation that has been reverted with <command>&no-i18n-cmd_undo;</"
"command>()."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>पुनः कुर्वन्तु</guibutton> साधनपट्टिकाबटनस्य अनुरूपं भवति तथा च एकं कार्यं "
"पुनरावृत्तिं करोति यत् <command>&no-i18n-cmd_undo;</command>() इत्यनेन सह प्रत्यागतम् "
"अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3352 index.docbook:3368 index.docbook:3826
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_undo;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_undo;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3358
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_redo_all;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_पुनः_सर्व;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_redo_all;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_redo_all;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similar to <command>&no-i18n-cmd_redo;</command>(), but re-does as many "
"operations as possible."
msgstr ""
"<command>&no-i18n-cmd_redo;</command>() इत्यस्य सदृशं, परन्तु यथासम्भवं अधिकानि "
"कार्याणि पुनः करोति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3374
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_reenable_dna;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_पुनः सक्षम_डीएनए;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_reenable_dna;</command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_reenable_dna;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some message boxes offer the possibility to prevent them from appearing "
"again (<quote>do not ask again</quote>). This command makes all of them "
"appear again."
msgstr ""
"केचन सन्देशपेटिकाः पुनः तेषां निवारणस्य सम्भावनां प्रददति (<quote>पुनः मा पृच्छतु</quote>) "
"। एतेन आदेशेन सर्वे पुनः दृश्यन्ते ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3386
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_reset_toolbars;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_reset_toolbars;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_reset_toolbars;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_reset_toolbars;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Resets all toolbar settings, like location, icon size and text location back "
"to defaults."
msgstr ""
"सर्वाणि साधनपट्टिकासेटिंग्स्, यथा स्थानं, चिह्नस्य आकारः, पाठस्थानं च पूर्वनिर्धारितरूपेण पुनः "
"सेट् करोति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3397
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_revert;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_revert;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3399
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_revert;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_revert;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reverts the currently loaded file back to the last saved state, discarding "
"all changes that are not saved."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमानं लोड् कृतं सञ्चिकां पुनः अन्तिम-रक्षित-स्थितौ प्रत्यागच्छति, ये परिवर्तनानि न "
"रक्षितानि तानि परित्यजति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3408
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_rewind;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_rewind;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3410
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_rewind;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_rewind;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the <guibutton>Rewind</guibutton> toolbar button. If the "
"playback is currently running, it skips backward by 1/10 of the visible "
"range. If the playback is not running, this does the same as the command "
"<command>&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_left;</command>()."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Rewind</guibutton> इति साधनपट्टिकाबटनस्य अनुरूपं भवति । यदि प्लेबैक् "
"सम्प्रति प्रचलति तर्हि दृश्यमानस्य परिधिस्य १/१० पृष्ठतः लङ्घयति । यदि प्लेबैक् न चाल्यते "
"तर्हि एतत् <command>&no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_left;</command>() इत्यस्य आदेशस्य "
"समानं करोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3420
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_view_scroll_left\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-"
"cmd_view_scroll_left;</command>()</link>, <link linkend=\"cmd_sect_forward"
"\"><command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_forward;</command>()</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_view_scroll_left\"><command>&amp;no-i18n-tag;&amp;"
"no-i18n-cmd_view_scroll_left;</command> () ९.</link> , ९.<link linkend="
"\"cmd_sect_forward\"><command> &amp;no-i18n-tag;&amp;no-i18n-cmd_forward;</"
"command> () ९.</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3428
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;s"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;s"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3431
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_save;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_save;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3433
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_save;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_save;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Corresponds to the <guibutton>Save</guibutton> toolbar button. Saves the "
"current file if it has modifications. If the file does not already have a "
"name (&eg; a file that has just been created and does not yet have a file "
"name), this command does the same as <command>&no-i18n-cmd_saveas;</"
"command>()."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Save</guibutton> इति साधनपट्टिकाबटनस्य अनुरूपं भवति । यदि वर्तमानसञ्चिकां "
"परिवर्तनं भवति तर्हि रक्षति । यदि सञ्चिकायाः पूर्वमेव नाम नास्ति (&उदा. सद्यः निर्मितः "
"सञ्चिका अद्यापि सञ्चिकानाम नास्ति), तर्हि एषः आदेशः <command>&no-i18n-cmd_saveas;</"
"command>() इत्यस्य समानं करोति । ."

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3444
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_saveas;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_saveas;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3450
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_saveas;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_saveas;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3452
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_saveas;</"
"command>([<replaceable>filename</replaceable>])"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_saveas;</"
"command>([<प्रतिस्थापनीय>सञ्चिकानाम</प्रतिस्थापनीय>])"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3453
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Saves the currently opened file under a given file name. If no file name is "
"given as parameter, a dialog will be shown to select the directory and to "
"enter a file name."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमानं उद्घाटितां सञ्चिकां दत्तसञ्चिकानाम्ना रक्षति । यदि पैरामीटर् रूपेण कोऽपि "
"सञ्चिकानाम न दत्तं तर्हि निर्देशिकां चिन्वितुं सञ्चिकानाम प्रविष्टुं च संवादः दर्शितः भविष्यति "
"।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3461
#, no-c-format
msgid "file name for saving (optional)"
msgstr "रक्षणार्थं सञ्चिकानाम (वैकल्पिकम्)"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3466
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_saveselect;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_saveselect;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_saveselect;</command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_saveselect;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command does the same as <command>&no-i18n-cmd_save;</command>(), but "
"saves only the currently selected range and the activated tracks instead of "
"the whole file."
msgstr ""
"एषः आदेशः <command>&no-i18n-cmd_save;</command>() इत्यस्य समानं करोति, परन्तु "
"सम्पूर्णसञ्चिकायाः स्थाने केवलं वर्तमानचयनितपरिधिं सक्रियपटलं च रक्षति ।"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3477
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_save;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_save;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3483
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_select_gui_type;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_चयन_gui_प्रकार;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3485
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_select_gui_type;</"
"command>(<replaceable>mode</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-cmd_select_gui_type;</"
"command>(<प्रतिस्थापनीय>मोड</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3486
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a &GUI; mode, which can be either SDI, MDI or Tab mode. Please be "
"aware that this change will immediately take effect!"
msgstr ""
"एकं &GUI चिनोतु; mode, यत् SDI, MDI अथवा Tab मोड् वा भवितुम् अर्हति । कृपया अवगच्छन्तु "
"यत् एषः परिवर्तनः तत्क्षणमेव प्रभावी भविष्यति!"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3494
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"name of the mode, must be either <quote>SDI</quote>, <quote>MDI</quote> or "
"<quote>TAB</quote>."
msgstr ""
"मोडस्य नाम, <quote>SDI</quote>, <quote>MDI</quote> अथवा <quote>TAB</quote> वा "
"भवितुमर्हति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3502
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_all;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_all;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3504 index.docbook:3521
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_all;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_all;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3505
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mark all tracks <quote>enabled</quote>. This is the same as calling the "
"command <command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_on;</command>() for "
"all existing tracks."
msgstr ""
"सर्वाणि पटलानि <quote>सक्षमम्</quote> इति चिह्नं कुर्वन्तु । एतत् सर्वेषां "
"विद्यमानपट्टिकानां कृते <command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_on;</"
"command>() इति आदेशं आह्वयितुं समानम् अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3513
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_on;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_on;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3519
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_invert;"
msgstr "& no-i18n-cmd_select_track_invert;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3522
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Invert the <quote>enabled</quote> state of all tracks. This is the same as "
"calling the command <command>&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_toggle;</command>() "
"for all existing tracks."
msgstr ""
"सर्वेषां पटलानां <quote>सक्षम</quote> अवस्थां विपर्यययन्तु । एतत् सर्वेषां विद्यमानपट्टिकानां "
"कृते <command>&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_toggle;</command>() इति आदेशं आह्वयितुं "
"समानम् अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3531
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_toggle;</command>()"
msgstr "<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_toggle;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3537
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_none;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_none;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3539
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_none;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_none;</"
"command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3540
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mark all tracks <quote>disabled</quote>. This is the same as calling the "
"command <command>&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_off;</command>() for all existing "
"tracks."
msgstr ""
"सर्वाणि पटलानि <quote>अक्षमम्</quote> इति चिह्नं कुर्वन्तु । एतत् सर्वेषां "
"विद्यमानपट्टिकानां कृते <command>&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_off;</command>() इति "
"आदेशं आह्वयितुं समानम् अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3548
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_off;</command>()"
msgstr "<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_off;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3554
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_off;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_चयन_पटल_बंद;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3556
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_off;</"
"command>(<replaceable>index</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_off;</"
"command>(<प्रतिस्थापनीय>सूचकाङ्क</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3557
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Disables a single track, so that it does not get affected by most operations."
msgstr "एकं पटलं निष्क्रियं करोति, येन अधिकांशक्रियाभिः प्रभावितः न भवति ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3564 index.docbook:3578 index.docbook:3593
#, no-c-format
msgid "index of the track, starting with zero"
msgstr "शून्यात् आरभ्य पटलस्य अनुक्रमणिका"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3569
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_on;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_चयन_पटल_चालू;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3571
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_on;</"
"command>(<replaceable>index</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_on;</"
"command>(<प्रतिस्थापनीय>सूचकाङ्क</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3572
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enables a single track, so that it gets affected by all operations."
msgstr "एकं पटलं सक्षमं करोति, येन सर्वैः कार्यैः प्रभावितः भवति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3583
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_toggle;"
msgstr "& no-i18n-cmd_select_track_toggle;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3585
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_toggle;</"
"command>(<replaceable>index</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-cmd_select_track_toggle;</"
"command>(<प्रतिस्थापनीय>सूचकाङ्क</प्रतिस्थापनीय>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3586
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enables a track if it is currently disabled, or disables it if it is "
"currently enabled."
msgstr ""
"यदि सम्प्रति अक्षमः अस्ति तर्हि पटलं सक्षमं करोति, अथवा सम्प्रति सक्षमं चेत् अक्षमं करोति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3598
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_selectall;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_selectall;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectall;</command>()"
msgstr "&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectall;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects the range of the whole signal, from the first to the last sample."
msgstr "प्रथमतः अन्तिमनमूनपर्यन्तं सम्पूर्णसंकेतस्य परिधिं चिनोति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3609
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_selectnext;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_selectnext;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectnext;</command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectnext;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3612
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects a range of samples that starts right after the current selection, "
"using the same length as the current selection. The selection is "
"automatically clipped to the end of the signal. For example: if you have "
"selected samples 1000 ... 1019, then the result will be a selection from "
"sample 1020 ... 1039."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमानचयनस्य अनन्तरमेव आरभ्यमाणानां नमूनानां श्रेणीं चिनोति, वर्तमानचयनस्य समानदीर्घतायाः "
"उपयोगेन । चयनं स्वयमेव संकेतस्य अन्ते यावत् क्लिप् भवति । यथा : यदि भवान् नमूनानि 1000 ... "
"1019 चयनितवान् अस्ति, तर्हि परिणामः नमूना 1020 ... 1039 तः चयनं भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3622
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectprev;</command>()"
msgstr "<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectprev;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3628
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_selectnextlabels;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_selectnexlabels;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3630
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectnextlabels;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectnexlabels;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3631
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects a range of samples between the next two labels after the current "
"selection. If nothing is selected, it selects from the start of the signal "
"up to the first label. Otherwise the left border of the new selection will "
"be the position of first label after the selection (or the last label if "
"there are no more labels right from the selection), and the right border of "
"the new selection will be the first label after the left border of the new "
"selection (or the end of the signal if there is none). This command returns "
"an error when there are no labels at all."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमानचयनस्य अनन्तरं अग्रिमयोः लेबलयोः मध्ये नमूनानां श्रेणीं चिनोति । यदि किमपि न "
"चिनोति तर्हि संकेतस्य आरम्भात् प्रथमलेबलपर्यन्तं चयनं करोति । अन्यथा नूतनचयनस्य वामसीमा "
"चयनस्य अनन्तरं प्रथमलेबलस्य स्थानं भविष्यति (अथवा अन्तिमलेबलं यदि चयनात् एव अधिकानि "
"लेबलानि नास्ति), तथा च नूतनचयनस्य दक्षिणसीमा च प्रथमं लेबलं भविष्यति नूतनचयनस्य वामसीमा "
"(अथवा संकेतस्य अन्तः यदि नास्ति)। यदा लेबल् सर्वथा नास्ति तदा एषः आदेशः त्रुटिं "
"प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3645
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectprevlabels;</command>()"
msgstr "<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectprevlabels;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3651
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_selectnone;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_selectnone;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3653
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectnone;</command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectnone;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3654
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resets the selection to zero length."
msgstr "चयनं शून्यदीर्घतायां पुनः सेट् करोति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3661
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_selectprev;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_चयनपूर्व;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectprev;</command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectprev;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3664
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects a range of samples that starts left from the current selection, "
"using the same length as the current selection. The selection is "
"automatically clipped to the start of the signal. For example: if you have "
"selected samples 1000 ... 1019, then the result will be a selection from "
"sample 980 ... 999."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमानचयनात् वामभागे आरभ्यमाणानां नमूनानां श्रेणीं चिनोति, वर्तमानचयनस्य समानदीर्घतायाः "
"उपयोगेन । चयनं स्वयमेव संकेतस्य आरम्भं यावत् क्लिप् भवति । यथा : यदि भवान् नमूनानि "
"1000 ... 1019 चयनितवान् अस्ति, तर्हि परिणामः नमूना 980 ... 999 तः चयनं भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3674
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectnext;</command>()"
msgstr "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectnext;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3680
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_selectprevlabels;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_selectprevlabels;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3682
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectprevlabels;</"
"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectprevlabels;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects a range of samples between the previous two labels before the "
"current selection. If nothing is selected, it selects from the start of the "
"signal up to the first label. Otherwise the right border of the new "
"selection will be the position of first label before the selection (or the "
"first label if there are no more labels left from the selection), and the "
"left border of the new selection will be the first label before the right "
"border of the new selection (or the start of the signal if there is none). "
"This command returns an error when there are no labels at all."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमानचयनात् पूर्वं पूर्वद्वयलेबलयोः मध्ये नमूनानां श्रेणीं चिनोति । यदि किमपि न चिनोति "
"तर्हि संकेतस्य आरम्भात् प्रथमलेबलपर्यन्तं चयनं करोति । अन्यथा नूतनचयनस्य दक्षिणसीमा चयनात् "
"पूर्वं प्रथमलेबलस्य स्थानं भविष्यति (अथवा प्रथमलेबलं यदि चयनात् अधिकानि लेबलानि न "
"अवशिष्टानि सन्ति), तथा च नूतनचयनस्य वामसीमा प्रथमलेबलस्य पूर्वं भविष्यति नूतनचयनस्य "
"दक्षिणसीमा (अथवा संकेतस्य आरम्भः यदि कोऽपि नास्ति)। यदा लेबल् सर्वथा नास्ति तदा एषः "
"आदेशः त्रुटिं प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:3697
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectnextlabels;</command>()"
msgstr "<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selectnexlabels;</command>()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3703
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-cmd_selecttoleft;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-cmd_selecttoleft;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<command>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selecttoleft;</command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_selecttoleft;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3706
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the start of the selection to the start of the signal, the end of the "
"current selection stays unchanged."
msgstr ""
