"command>()"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-cmd_syntax;<आदेश>&no-i18n-tag;&no-i18n-cmd_view_zoom_all;</command>()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3964
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adjusts the zoom factor so that the complete signal is visible in the "
"current view."
msgstr "जूम् कारकं समायोजयति येन वर्तमानदृश्ये सम्पूर्णः संकेतः दृश्यते ।"

