#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_band_pass; (Band Pass Filter)"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगइन_बैंड_पास; (बैण्ड पास फ़िल्टर)"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:4570
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Band Pass Filter Plugin"
msgstr "Band Pass Filter Plugin इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट्"

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:4577
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_band_pass;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगइन_बैण्ड_पास;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4586
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Applies a simple band pass filter to the current selection. A band pass lets "
"a certain range of frequencies around a <emphasis>center frequency</"
"emphasis> pass and filters out frequencies that are below or above the "
"center frequency by more than half of the <emphasis>bandwidth</emphasis> of "
"the filter."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमानचयनं प्रति सरलं बैण्ड्-पास्-छिद्रकं प्रयोजयति । बैण्ड्-पास् <emphasis>केन्द्र-आवृत्ति</"
"emphasis> इत्यस्य परितः आवृत्तीनां निश्चितपरिधिं गन्तुं ददाति तथा च केन्द्र-आवृत्तितः अधः "
"वा उपरि वा आवृत्तिः फ़िल्टरस्य <emphasis>बैण्डविड्थ</emphasis> इत्यस्य आर्धाधिकेन फ़िल्टर "
"करोति ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4592
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The filter has grade two and is implemented as described in the book "
"<citetitle>\"An introduction to digital filter theory\"</citetitle> by "
"<author> <personname> <firstname>Julius O.</firstname> <surname>Smith</"
"surname> </personname> </author> and in Moore's book, where the normalized "
"version from Moore's book is used."
msgstr ""
"फ़िल्टरस्य द्वितीयश्रेणी अस्ति तथा च <author> <personname> <firstname>Julius O.</"
"firstname> <surname>Smith< इत्यनेन <citetitle>\"An introduction to digital "
"filter theory\"</citetitle> इति पुस्तके यथा वर्णितं तथा कार्यान्वितम् /surname> </"
"personname> </author> तथा मूर् पुस्तके, यत्र मूर् पुस्तकात् सामान्यीकृतसंस्करणस्य उपयोगः "
"भवति ।"

