#: index.docbook:5719
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_newsignal;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगइन_न्यूसिग्नल;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5728
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provides a dialog to create a new file. Please refer to the section <link "
"linkend=\"newsignal\" endterm=\"sect_title_newsignal\"></link> in this "
"manual for more information."
msgstr ""
"नूतनसञ्चिकां निर्मातुं संवादं प्रदाति । कृपया खण्डं पश्यन्तु<link linkend=\"newsignal\" "
"endterm=\"sect_title_newsignal\"></link> अधिकविवरणार्थं अस्मिन् पुस्तिकायां ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5739
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_newsignal\" endterm=\"cmd_title_newsignal\"></link>,"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"cmd_sect_newsignal\" endterm=\"cmd_title_newsignal\"></link>,"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5748
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_noise; (Noise Generator)"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगिन्_कोलाहल; (कोलाहल जनरेटर)"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:5756
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Noise Generator Plugin"
msgstr "शोर जनरेटर प्लगिन् इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट्"

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:5763
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_noise;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगिन्_कोलाहल;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5772
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adds some amount of white noise to the current selection. The amount of "
"noise can be selected between zero (no noise, original remains unchanged) "
"and one (original will be replaced by 100% noise)."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमानचयनं प्रति किञ्चित् श्वेतकोलाहलं योजयति । शून्यस्य (कोऽपि कोलाहलः नास्ति, मूलं "
"अपरिवर्तितं तिष्ठति) एकस्य (मूलस्य स्थाने शतप्रतिशतम् कोलाहलः भविष्यति) मध्ये कोलाहलस्य "
"परिमाणं चयनं कर्तुं शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:5785
#, no-c-format
msgid "level"
msgstr "स्तर"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5787
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Noise level, always has to be a floating point number above zero and below "
"or equal to one."
msgstr ""
"कोलाहलस्तरः, सर्वदा शून्यात् उपरि प्लवमानबिन्दुसङ्ख्या भवितुमर्हति तथा च एकस्य अधः वा समः "
"वा ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:5807
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the noise value as percentage of the amplitude, from 0 to 100."
msgstr "0 तः 100 पर्यन्तं आयामस्य प्रतिशतरूपेण कोलाहलमूल्यं प्रविशन्तु ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:5814
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the noise in decibel, from -21 dB to 0 dB."
msgstr "-21 dB तः 0 dB पर्यन्तं डेसिबेल् मध्ये कोलाहलं प्रविशन्तु ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5831
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_normalize; (Normalizer)"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगइन_सामान्यीकरण; (सामान्यीकरण)"

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:5835
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_normalize;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगइन_सामान्यीकरण;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5844
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Normalizes the volume level of the current selection. Use this if the volume "
"of your signal is too low or too high."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमानचयनस्य आयतनस्तरं सामान्यं करोति । यदि भवतः संकेतस्य मात्रा अत्यधिकं न्यूनं वा अत्यधिकं "
"वा भवति तर्हि एतस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5848
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The algorithm is taken from the <citetitle>normalize</citetitle> project, "
"and was originally written by <link linkend=\"author_Chris_Vaill\"> <author> "
"<personname> <firstname>Chris</firstname> <surname>Vaill</surname> </"
"personname> </author> </link>."
msgstr ""
"अल्गोरिदम् इत्यस्मात् गृह्यते<citetitle> normalize</citetitle> परियोजना, मूलतः च "
"लिखितम् आसीत्<link linkend=\"author_Chris_Vaill"
"\"><author><personname><firstname> क्रिसः</firstname><surname> वैल</surname></"
"personname></author></link> ."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5866
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_notch_filter; (Notch Filter)"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगइन_नॉच_फिल्टर; (Notch Filter)"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:5874
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Notch Filter Plugin"
msgstr "Notch Filter Plugin इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट्"

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:5881
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_notch_filter;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगइन_नॉच_फिल्टर;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5890
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Applies a notch filter to the current selection. A notch filter removes a "
"small range of frequencies around a <emphasis>center frequency</emphasis> "
"and lets all other frequencies below and above the center frequency by more "
"than half of the <emphasis>bandwidth</emphasis> pass."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमानचयनं प्रति notch filter इत्येतत् प्रयोजयति । एकः खाँच-छिद्रकः <emphasis>केन्द्र-"
"आवृत्ति</emphasis> इत्यस्य परितः आवृत्तीनां लघुपरिधिं निष्कासयति तथा च केन्द्र-आवृत्तेः अधः "
"उपरि च अन्येषां सर्वेषां आवृत्तीनां <emphasis>बैण्डविड्थ्</emphasis> इत्यस्य आर्धाधिकं पारं "
"गन्तुं ददाति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5897
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use this to filter out single distortion frequencies."
msgstr "एकविकृतिआवृत्तिः छानयितुं एतस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5900
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The filter has grade two and is based on the implementation of <link linkend="
"\"author_Juhana_Sadeharju\"> <author> <personname> <firstname>Juhana</"
"firstname> <surname>Sadeharju</surname> </personname> </author> </link>."
msgstr ""
"फ़िल्टरस्य द्वितीयश्रेणी अस्ति तथा च तस्य कार्यान्वयनम् आधारितम् अस्ति<link linkend="
"\"author_Juhana_Sadeharju\"><author><personname><firstname> जुहाना</"
"firstname><surname> सदेहर्जु</surname></personname></author></link> ."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:5941
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_pitch_shift; (Pitch Shift)"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगइन_पिच_शिफ्ट; (पिच शिफ्ट)"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:5949
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Pitch Shift Plugin"
msgstr "Pitch Shift Plugin इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट्"

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:5956
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_pitch_shift;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगइन_पिच_शिफ्ट;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5965
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The pitch shift effect modifies the signal by changing the speed of the "
"content, but with keeping the original length. You can select the relative "
"speed either by factor from 1/10 to x5, or as a percentage from 1% to 400% "
"of the original speed."
msgstr ""
"पिच शिफ्ट इफेक्ट् सामग्रीयाः गतिं परिवर्त्य, परन्तु मूलदीर्घतां धारयित्वा संकेतं परिवर्तयति । "
"सापेक्षवेगं 1/10 तः x5 पर्यन्तं कारकद्वारा, अथवा मूलवेगस्य 1% तः 400% पर्यन्तं प्रतिशतरूपेण "
"वा चयनं कर्तुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5971
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A speed factor below 1.0 pitches the signal down (lower voice, makes voices "
"sound older), factor 1.0 does no change and a factor above 1.0 pitches the "
"signal up (higher voice, Mickey Mouse effect)."
msgstr ""
"१.० तः न्यूनः गतिकारकः संकेतं अधः पिच करोति (अधः स्वरः, स्वराः प्राचीनाः ध्वनिं "
"कुर्वन्ति), कारकः १.० परिवर्तनं न करोति तथा च १.० तः उपरि कारकः संकेतं उपरि पिच "
"करोति (उच्चतरः स्वरः, मिक्की माउस् प्रभावः)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:5977
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The implementation is based on the work of <link linkend="
"\"author_Jeff_Tranter\"> <author> <personname> <firstname>Jeff</firstname> "
"<surname>Tranter</surname> </personname> </author> </link> and <link linkend="
"\"author_Stefan_Westerfeld\"> <author> <personname> <firstname>Stefan</"
"firstname> <surname>Westerfeld</surname> </personname> </author> </link>"
msgstr ""
"कार्यान्वयनम् इत्यस्य कार्यम् आधारितम् अस्ति<link linkend=\"author_Jeff_Tranter"
"\"><author><personname><firstname> जेफ्</firstname><surname> Tranter</"
"surname></personname></author></link> तथा<link linkend="
"\"author_Stefan_Westerfeld\"><author><personname><firstname> स्टीफन्</"
"firstname><surname> वेस्टर्फेल्ड्</surname></personname></author></link>"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6004
#, no-c-format
msgid "speed"
msgstr "गति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6006
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Factor for changing the speed, has to be a floating point number between "
"0.001 and 4.0."
msgstr "गतिं परिवर्तयितुं कारकः, 0.001 तः 4.0 पर्यन्तं प्लवमानबिन्दुसङ्ख्या भवितुमर्हति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6015
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Frequency internally used by the filter in Hz, has to be between 2.0 and "
"10.0."
msgstr "Hz मध्ये फ़िल्टरेन आन्तरिकरूपेण प्रयुक्ता आवृत्तिः, 2.0 तः 10.0 पर्यन्तं भवितुमर्हति ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:6035
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the speed value as factor from 1/10 to x5."
msgstr "1/10 तः x5 पर्यन्तं गतिमूल्यं कारकरूपेण प्रविशन्तु ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:6042
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the speed value as percentage from 1 to 400."
msgstr "गतिमूल्यं 1 तः 400 पर्यन्तं प्रतिशतरूपेण प्रविशन्तु ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:6059
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_playback; (Playback)"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगिन्_प्लेबैक; (प्लेबैक)"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:6067
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Playback Plugin"
msgstr "प्लेबैक प्लगिन् इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट्"

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:6074
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_playback;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगिन्_प्लेबैक;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6083
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provides a dialog to set up the playback parameters. Please refer to the "
"section <link linkend=\"playback\" endterm=\"sect_title_playback\"></link> "
"in this manual for more information."
msgstr ""
"प्लेबैक पैरामीटर्स् सेट् कर्तुं संवादं प्रदाति । कृपया खण्डं पश्यन्तु<link linkend=\"playback\" "
"endterm=\"sect_title_playback\"></link> अधिकसूचनार्थं अस्मिन् पुस्तिकायां।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6096
#, no-c-format
msgid "playback method"
msgstr "प्लेबैक विधि"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6098
#, no-c-format
msgid "The method used for playback, see <filename>PlayBackParam.h</filename>."
msgstr "प्लेबैक् कृते प्रयुक्ता विधिः, <filename>PlayBackParam.h</filename> पश्यन्तु ।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6105
#, no-c-format
msgid "playback device"
msgstr "प्लेबैक यन्त्रम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A string that determines the playback device or channel. The meaning depends "
"on the playback method."
msgstr ""
"प्लेबैक-यन्त्रं वा चैनलं वा निर्धारयति इति स्ट्रिंग् । अर्थः वादनविधिना आश्रितः भवति ।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6115 index.docbook:6270
#, no-c-format
msgid "channels"
msgstr "चैनल्स्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number of channels to use for playback, currently supports only 1 (mono) "
"or 2 (stereo)."
msgstr ""
"प्लेबैक् कृते उपयोक्तुं शक्यमाणानां चैनलानां संख्या, सम्प्रति केवलं १ (मोनो) अथवा २ (स्टीरियो) "
"समर्थयति ।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6124 index.docbook:6304
#, no-c-format
msgid "bits per sample"
msgstr "प्रति नमूना बिट्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number of bits per sample for playback, should be 8, 16, 24 or 32. "
"Depends on the playback method and the playback device."
msgstr ""
"प्लेबैक् कृते प्रति नमूना बिट्-सङ्ख्या, ८, १६, २४ वा ३२ वा भवितुमर्हति प्लेबैक्-विधेः प्लेबैक-"
"यन्त्रस्य च उपरि निर्भरं भवति ।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6135 index.docbook:6321
#, no-c-format
msgid "buffer size"
msgstr "बफर आकारः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Determines the size of the playback buffer, used as exponent for calculating "
"the real buffer size as 2^n, &eg; setting this to 16 gives a buffer size of "
"2^16 = 64 kB."
msgstr ""
"प्लेबैक् बफरस्य आकारं निर्धारयति, यस्य उपयोगः वास्तविकबफर आकारस्य गणनायै घातांकरूपेण भवति "
"यथा 2^n, &eg; एतत् 16 इति सेट् कृत्वा 2^16 = 64 kB इत्यस्य बफर आकारः प्राप्यते ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:6152
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_record; (Record)"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगइन_अभिलेख; (अभिलेख)"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:6160
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Record Plugin"
msgstr "Record Plugin इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट्"

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:6167
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_record;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगइन_अभिलेख;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provides a dialog to set up the record parameters and to do a recording. "
"Please refer to the section <link linkend=\"recording\" endterm="
"\"sect_title_recording\"></link> in this manual for more information."
msgstr ""
"रिकार्ड् पैरामीटर्स् सेट् कर्तुं रिकार्डिङ्ग् कर्तुं च संवादं प्रदाति । कृपया खण्डं पश्यन्तु<link "
"linkend=\"recording\" endterm=\"sect_title_recording\"></link> अधिकविवरणार्थं "
"अस्मिन् पुस्तिकायां ।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6189
#, no-c-format
msgid "recording method"
msgstr "रिकार्डिंग विधि"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6191
#, no-c-format
msgid "The method used for recording, see <filename>RecordParams.h</filename>."
msgstr "अभिलेखनार्थं प्रयुक्ता विधिः, <filename>RecordParams.h</filename> पश्यन्तु ।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6198
#, no-c-format
msgid "pre recording enabled"
msgstr "पूर्व रिकॉर्डिंग् सक्षमम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6200
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable/disable pre recording (1 if enabled, 0 if disabled)."
msgstr "पूर्व-अभिलेखनं सक्षमं/अक्षमं कुर्वन्तु (1 यदि सक्षमम् अस्ति, 0 यदि अक्षमम् अस्ति)।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6206
#, no-c-format
msgid "pre recording time"
msgstr "पूर्व रिकार्डिंग समय"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of seconds for pre recording."
msgstr "पूर्व-अभिलेखनार्थं सेकण्ड्-सङ्ख्या ।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6214
#, no-c-format
msgid "limit recording time"
msgstr "रिकार्डिङ्गसमयं सीमितं कुर्वन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable/disable limiting of recording time (1 if limited, 0 if not limited)."
msgstr "रिकार्डिङ्गसमयस्य सीमां सक्षमं/अक्षमं कुर्वन्तु (1 यदि सीमितं, 0 यदि सीमितं नास्ति)।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6222
#, no-c-format
msgid "recording time"
msgstr "रिकार्डिङ्ग समय"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Duration of the recording in seconds."
msgstr "रिकार्डिङ्गस्य अवधिः सेकेण्ड्-मात्रेषु ।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6230
#, no-c-format
msgid "use starting time"
msgstr "आरम्भसमयस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6232
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable/disable starting time (1 if used, 0 if not used)."
msgstr "आरम्भसमयं सक्षमं/अक्षमं कुर्वन्तु (1 यदि प्रयुक्तं, 0 यदि न प्रयुक्तम्)।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6238
#, no-c-format
msgid "starting time"
msgstr "आरम्भसमयः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6240
#, no-c-format
msgid "Date/time to start the recording, in ISO format."
msgstr "रिकार्डिङ्ग् आरभ्यतुं तिथिः/समयः, ISO प्रारूपेण ।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6246
#, no-c-format
msgid "use trigger level"
msgstr "ट्रिगर स्तरस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6248
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable/disable trigger level (1 if used, 0 if not used)."
msgstr "ट्रिगरस्तरं सक्षमं/अक्षमं कुर्वन्तु (1 यदि उपयुज्यते, 0 यदि न प्रयुक्तम्)।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6254
#, no-c-format
msgid "trigger level"
msgstr "trigger level"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6256
#, no-c-format
msgid "Trigger level in percent."
msgstr "प्रतिशते ट्रिगर स्तरः।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6262
#, no-c-format
msgid "recording device"
