#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sample format to use for storing the samples, see <link linkend=\"sample-"
"formats\">section about sample formats</link>."
msgstr ""
"नमूनानां संग्रहणार्थं उपयोक्तुं नमूनास्वरूपं, पश्यन्तु<link linkend=\"sample-formats\"> "
"नमूनास्वरूपाणां विषये विभागः</link> ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6306
#, no-c-format
msgid "The number of bits per sample for recording, should be 8, 16, 24 or 32."
msgstr "अभिलेखनार्थं प्रतिनमूना बिट्-सङ्ख्या, ८, १६, २४ वा ३२ वा भवितुमर्हति ।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6313
