#: index.docbook:6361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the recording dialog and select the <guilabel>Source</guilabel> tab."
msgstr "रिकार्डिङ्ग् संवादं उद्घाट्य <guilabel>Source</guilabel> ट्याब् चिनोतु ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:6366
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;<command>start_now</command>"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;<command>अधुना_प्रारम्भ</command>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:6367
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open the recording dialog and directly start recording."
msgstr "रिकार्डिङ्ग् संवादं उद्घाट्य प्रत्यक्षतया रिकार्डिङ्ग् आरभत ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:6385
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_reverse; (Reverse)"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगइन_विपरीत; (विपरीत)"

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:6389
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_reverse;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगइन_विपरीत;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6398
#, no-c-format
msgid "This simple effect reverses the content of the current selection."
msgstr "एषः सरलः प्रभावः वर्तमानचयनस्य सामग्रीं विपर्ययति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:6407
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_samplerate; (Sample Rate Conversion)"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगइन_नमूनाकरण; (नमूना दररूपान्तरणम्)"

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:6411
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_samplerate;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगइन_नमूनाकरण;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6420
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changes the sample rate of the current selection or the whole signal."
msgstr "वर्तमानचयनस्य अथवा सम्पूर्णसंकेतस्य नमूनादरं परिवर्तयति ।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6431
#, no-c-format
msgid "new rate"
msgstr "नवीन दर"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6433
#, no-c-format
msgid "The new sample rate in samples per second (floating point value)."
msgstr "प्रति सेकण्ड् नमूनासु नूतनं नमूनादरं (प्लवमानबिन्दुमूल्यम्)।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:6440
#, no-c-format
msgid "<replaceable>mode</replaceable> (optional)"
msgstr "<replaceable>mode</replaceable> (वैकल्पिकम्)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6442
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this parameter is used and set to the value \"<literal>all</literal>\", "
"then this effect will be applied to the whole signal. Otherwise it will be "
"applied to the current selection only."
msgstr ""
"यदि एतत् पैरामीटर् उपयुज्यते तथा च \"<literal>all</literal>\" इति मूल्ये सेट् भवति, "
"तर्हि एषः प्रभावः समग्रसंकेते प्रयुक्तः भविष्यति । अन्यथा वर्तमानचयनमात्रे एव प्रयुक्तं "
"भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:6458
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_saveblocks; (Save Blocks)"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगइन_सेवब्लॉक; (खण्डान् रक्षन्तु)"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:6466
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Save Blocks Plugin"
msgstr "Save Blocks प्लगिन् इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट्"

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:6473
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_saveblocks;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगइन_सेवब्लॉक;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6482
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Saves all sections between markers, each into a separate file. Each file is "
"given a name that can be customized by using a pattern that can contain the "
"original file name, an index and the number of sections."
msgstr ""
"मार्करयोः मध्ये सर्वान् विभागान् रक्षति, प्रत्येकं पृथक् सञ्चिकायां । प्रत्येकं सञ्चिकां नाम दत्तं "
"भवति यत् मूलसञ्चिकानाम, अनुक्रमणिका, विभागसङ्ख्या च समाविष्टुं शक्नोति इति प्रतिमानस्य "
"उपयोगेन अनुकूलितुं शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6488
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is also allowed that the file name pattern contains forward slashes as "
"path separators, which allows saving the sections into different sub "
"directories. Please note that all whitespace characters around such path "
"separators are silently removed, to avoid creation of directory names which "
"begin or end with a whitespace."
msgstr ""
"इदमपि अनुमतं यत् सञ्चिकानामप्रतिरूपेण मार्गविभाजकरूपेण अग्रे स्लैशाः सन्ति, येन विभागान् भिन्न-"
"उपनिर्देशिकासु रक्षितुं शक्यते । कृपया ज्ञातव्यं यत् एतादृशमार्गविभाजकानाम् परितः सर्वे "
"श्वेतस्थानवर्णाः मौनेन निष्कासिताः भवन्ति, येन श्वेतस्थानेन आरभ्यन्ते वा समाप्ताः वा "
"निर्देशिकानामनिर्माणं न भवति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6505
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A pattern that will be used for creating the names of the files. It can "
"contain the following wildcards which will be replaced by the corresponding "
"content when creating the final file name:"
msgstr ""
"एकं प्रतिरूपं यत् सञ्चिकानां नामनिर्माणार्थं उपयुज्यते । अस्मिन् निम्नलिखित वाइल्डकार्ड्स् भवितुं "
"शक्नुवन्ति येषां स्थाने अन्तिमसञ्चिकानाम निर्माय तत्सम्बद्धा सामग्री भविष्यति:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:6522
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;<command>[%nr]</command>"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;<command>[%nr]</command> इति"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:6523
#, no-c-format
msgid "Will be replaced with the current index of the file to save."
msgstr "रक्षितुं सञ्चिकायाः वर्तमानसूचकाङ्केन प्रतिस्थाप्यते ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:6529
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;<command>[%count]</command>"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;<command>[%count]</command> इति"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:6530
#, no-c-format
msgid "Will be replaced with the number of sections that will be saved."
msgstr "येषां खण्डानां संख्या रक्षिता भविष्यति तेषां स्थाने प्रतिस्थाप्यते।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:6536
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;<command>[%total]</command>"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;<command>[%total]</command> इति"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:6537
#, no-c-format
msgid "Will be replaced with the index of the last file to save."
msgstr "रक्षितुं अन्तिमसञ्चिकायाः अनुक्रमणिकायाः स्थाने स्थापितं भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:6543
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;<command>[%filename]</command>"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;<command>[%सञ्चिकानाम]</command>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:6544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will be replaced with the base file name, without path and without extension."
msgstr "आधारसञ्चिकानाम्ना प्रतिस्थापितं भविष्यति, मार्गं विना विस्तारं विना च ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:6550
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&no-i18n-tag;<command>[%fileinfo{<replaceable>keyword</replaceable>}]</"
"command>"
msgstr ""
"&no-i18n-tag;<command>[%fileinfo{<प्रतिस्थापनीय>कीवर्ड</replaceable>}]</command>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:6551
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will be replaced with the content of a file information identified by "
"<replaceable>keyword</replaceable>. See section <link linkend=\"file-info-"
"list\" endterm=\"file-info-list-title\"></link> for a list of all available "
"keywords."
msgstr ""
"द्वारा चिह्नितायाः सञ्चिकासूचनायाः सामग्रीना प्रतिस्थापिता भविष्यति<replaceable> "
"कीवर्ड</replaceable> . खण्डं पश्यन्तु<link linkend=\"file-info-list\" endterm="
"\"file-info-list-title\"></link> सर्वेषां उपलब्धानां कीवर्ड-शब्दानां सूचीं कृते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All numeric wildcards can also contain a numerical argument after the "
"\"<literal>%</literal>\" and the identifier, to force a certain number of "
"digits. If the number is preceded by a <literal>0</literal> then the result "
"will contain leading zeroes, otherwise it will contain leading spaces."
msgstr ""
"सर्वेषु संख्यात्मकेषु वाइल्डकार्ड्-मध्ये \"<literal>%</literal>\" इत्यस्य पश्चात् संख्यात्मकं तर्कं "
"अपि भवितुं शक्नोति, परिचयकस्य च, निश्चितसङ्ख्यायाः अङ्कानां बाध्यतां कर्तुं । यदि संख्यायाः "
"पूर्वं <literal>0</literal> भवति तर्हि परिणामे अग्रणीः शून्याः भविष्यन्ति, अन्यथा तस्मिन् "
"अग्रणीस्थानानि भविष्यन्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6581
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Example: <command><literal>[%04nr]</literal></command> produces a number "
"between 0001 and 9999."
msgstr ""
"उदाहरणम् : <command><literal>[%04nr]</literal></command> 0001 तः 9999 पर्यन्तं "
"सङ्ख्यां उत्पादयति ।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6589
#, no-c-format
msgid "numbering mode"
msgstr "संख्याकरणविधिः"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6625
#, no-c-format
msgid "extension"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6627
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The file name extension to use for the saved blocks. This determines what "
"encoding is used."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6637
#, no-c-format
msgid "The location to export the saved blocks."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:6683
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_selectrange; (Select Range)"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगइन_चयनपरिधि; (परिधिं चिनोतु)"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:6691
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Select Range Plugin"
msgstr "Select Range Plugin इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट्"

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:6698
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_selectrange;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगइन_चयनपरिधि;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6707
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows a dialog to select a range of samples. The start and the length of the "
"selection can be set either by a time in milliseconds, in samples, or as a "
"percentage of the total length of the file."
msgstr ""
"नमूनानां श्रेणीं चिन्वितुं संवादं दर्शयति । चयनस्य आरम्भः दीर्घता च मिलीसेकेण्ड्-मात्रायां, "
"नमूनासु, सञ्चिकायाः कुलदीर्घतायाः प्रतिशतरूपेण वा सेट् कर्तुं शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6719
#, no-c-format
msgid "start mode"
msgstr "start mode"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6721
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Determines the units in which the <emphasis>start</emphasis> of the "
"selection will be given."
msgstr "चयनस्य <emphasis>प्रारम्भः</emphasis> येषु एककेषु दीयते इति निर्धारयति ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:6736 index.docbook:7136
#, no-c-format
msgid "milliseconds"
msgstr "मिलीसेकेण्ड्"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:6740 index.docbook:7140
#, no-c-format
msgid "samples"
msgstr "नमूनानि"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:6744 index.docbook:7144
#, no-c-format
msgid "percentage of the length of the file"
msgstr "सञ्चिकायाः दीर्घतायाः प्रतिशतं भवति"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6754
#, no-c-format
msgid "range mode"
msgstr "रेंज मोड"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6756
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Determines the units in which the <emphasis>length</emphasis> of the "
"selection will be given. See the description if the parameter "
"<parameter>start mode</parameter> for a list of possible values."
msgstr ""
"चयनस्य <emphasis>दीर्घता</emphasis> येषु एककेषु दीयते इति निर्धारयति । सम्भाव्यमूल्यानां "
"सूचीं कृते <parameter>start mode</parameter> इति पैरामीटर् चेत् विवरणं पश्यन्तु ।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6768
#, no-c-format
msgid "start"
msgstr "प्रारंभः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6770
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The start of the selection, in milliseconds, samples or percentage of the "
"length of the file, depending on the parameter <parameter>range mode</"
"parameter>."
msgstr ""
"चयनस्य आरम्भः, मिलीसेकेण्ड् मध्ये, नमूनानि अथवा सञ्चिकायाः दीर्घतायाः प्रतिशतं, पैरामीटर् "
"<parameter>range mode</parameter> इत्यस्य आधारेण ।"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6780 index.docbook:7153
#, no-c-format
msgid "length"
msgstr "दैर्घ्यम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6782
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The length of the selection, in milliseconds, samples or percentage of the "
"length of the file, depending on the parameter <parameter>range mode</"
"parameter>."
msgstr ""
"चयनस्य दीर्घता, मिलीसेकेण्ड् मध्ये, नमूनानि अथवा सञ्चिकायाः दीर्घतायाः प्रतिशतं, पैरामीटर् "
"<parameter>range mode</parameter> इत्यस्य आधारेण ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:6797
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_sonagram; (Sonagram)"
msgstr "&no-i18n-प्लगिन्_सोनाग्राम; (सोनाग्राम)"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:6805
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the setup dialog of the Sonagram Plugin"
