"License information, &eg;, <quote>All Rights Reserved</quote>, <quote>Any "
"Use Permitted</quote>, an URL to a license or the Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 "
"International (<quote>distributed under the terms of the Attribution-"
"ShareAlike 4.0 International License. See &url_cc_by_sa_4; for details</"
"quote>), &etc;"
msgstr ""
"अनुज्ञापत्रसूचना, &eg;, <quote>सर्वाधिकारः सुरक्षितः</quote>, <quote>किमपि उपयोगः "
"अनुमतः</quote>, अनुज्ञापत्रस्य URL अथवा Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International "
"(<quote>स्य नियमानाम् अन्तर्गतं वितरितम् Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 अन्तर्राष्ट्रीय "
"अनुज्ञापत्रं पश्यन्तु &url_cc_by_sa_4;"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7985
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Medium"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;माध्यमम्"

