"Op.68 &quot;Pastoral&quot;</quote>"
msgstr ""
"सञ्चिकायाः विषयस्य शीर्षकं संगृह्णाति । उदाहरणम् : <quote>सिम्फोनी सं.६, ओप.६८ &quot;"
"गोपालन&quot;</quote>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8029
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Opus Frame Length"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;ओपस फ्रेम लम्बाई"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8030
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opus Frame Length in ms (supported values are 2.5, 5, 10, 20, 40, or 60 ms)"
msgstr ""
"Opus Frame Length in ms (समर्थितमूल्यानि 2.5, 5, 10, 20, 40, अथवा 60 ms भवन्ति)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8036
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Organization"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;सङ्गठनम्"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8037
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Name of the organization producing the track (i.e. the <quote>record label</"
"quote>)"
msgstr "पटलं उत्पादयन्तः संस्थायाः नाम (अर्थात् <quote>अभिलेखलेबल</quote>) ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8043
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Original"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;मूलम्"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8044
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indicates whether the file is an original or a copy"
msgstr "सञ्चिका मूलं वा प्रतिलिपिः वा इति सूचयति"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8049
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Performer"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;निष्पादक"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8050
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The artist(s) who performed the work. In classical music this would be the "
"conductor, orchestra, soloists. In an audio book it would be the actor who "
"did the reading."
msgstr ""
"ये कलाकाराः (कलाकाराः) कार्यं कृतवन्तः। शास्त्रीयसङ्गीतस्य एषः सञ्चालकः, वाद्यसमूहः, "
"एकलवादकाः स्यात् । श्रव्यपुस्तके पठनं कृतवान् अभिनेता एव स्यात्।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8057
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Private"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;निजी"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8058
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indicates whether the subject is private"
msgstr "विषयः निजी अस्ति वा इति सूचयति"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8063
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Product"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;उत्पादः"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8064
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the name or the title the file was originally intended for. "
"Example: <quote>Linux audio collection</quote>"
msgstr ""
"सञ्चिकायाः मूलतः अभिप्रेतं नाम वा शीर्षकं वा निर्दिशति । उदाहरणम् : <quote>लिनक्स "
"श्रव्यसङ्ग्रह</quote>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8070
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Sample Format"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;नमूना प्रारूप"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8071
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Format used for storing the digitized audio samples. Example: <quote>32-bit "
"IEEE floating-point</quote>"
msgstr ""
"अङ्कीकृतश्रव्यनमूनानां संग्रहणार्थं प्रयुक्तं प्रारूपम् । उदाहरणम् : <quote>32-बिट् IEEE प्लवक-"
"बिन्दु</quote>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8077
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Sample Rate"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;नमूना दर"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8078
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of samples per second"
msgstr "प्रति सेकण्ड् नमूनानां संख्या"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8083
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Software"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;सॉफ्टवेयर"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8084
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Identifies the name of the software package used to create the file. "
"Example: <quote>Kwave v0.6.4-1</quote>"
msgstr ""
"सञ्चिकायाः निर्माणार्थं प्रयुक्तस्य सॉफ्टवेयर-सङ्कुलस्य नाम चिनोति । उदाहरणम् : "
"<quote>क्वावे v0.6.4-1</quote>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8090
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Source"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;स्रोत"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8091
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Identifies the name of the person or organization who supplied the original "
"subject of the file. Example: <quote>Chaotic Sound Research</quote>"
msgstr ""
"सञ्चिकायाः मूलविषयं यः व्यक्तिः अथवा संस्थायाः आपूर्तिं कृतवान् तस्य नाम चिनोति । "
"उदाहरणम् : <quote>अराजकध्वनिसंशोधन</quote>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8098
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Source form"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;स्रोत रूप"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8099
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Identifies the original form of the material that was digitized. Examples: "
"<quote>Record/Vinyl/90RPM</quote>, <quote>Audio DAT</quote>, <quote>tape/"
"CrO2/60min</quote>"
msgstr ""
"अङ्कीकृतस्य सामग्रीयाः मूलरूपं चिनोति । उदाहरणानि : <quote>अभिलेखः/विनिल/90RPM</"
"quote>, <quote>श्रव्य DAT</quote>, <quote>टेप/CrO2/60min</quote>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8106
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Subject"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;विषयः"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Describes the subject of the file. Example: <quote>Bird voices at early "
"morning</quote>"
msgstr "सञ्चिकायाः विषयं वर्णयति । उदाहरणम् : <quote>प्रातःकाले पक्षिस्वरः</quote>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8113
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Technician"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;तकनीशियन"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Identifies the technician who digitized the subject file. Example: "
"<quote>Torvalds, Linus</quote>"
msgstr ""
"विषयसञ्चिकां अङ्कीकृतवान् इति तकनीकिं चिनोति । उदाहरणम् : <quote>टोर्वल्ड्स्, लिनस्</"
"quote>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8120
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Track"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;ट्रैक"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8121
#, no-c-format
msgid "Track of the CD if the source was a CDROM."
msgstr "यदि स्रोतः CDROM आसीत् तर्हि CD इत्यस्य ट्रैक।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8126
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Tracks"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;पट्टिकाः"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of tracks of the CD if the source was a CDROM."
msgstr "यदि स्रोतः CDROM आसीत् तर्हि CD इत्यस्य पटलानां संख्या ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8132
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Channels"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;चैनल"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specifies the number of channels of the signal."
msgstr "संकेतस्य चैनलानां संख्यां निर्दिशति ।"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8138
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Base Quality"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;आधार गुणवत्ता"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Base quality of the compression in VBR mode"
msgstr "VBR मोड् मध्ये संपीडनस्य आधारगुणवत्ता"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"May be used to differentiate multiple versions of the same track title in a "
"single collection. (&eg; remix info)"
msgstr ""
"एकस्मिन् संग्रहे एकस्यैव पटलशीर्षकस्य बहुसंस्करणानाम् भेदं कर्तुं उपयोक्तुं शक्यते । (&eg; remix "
"info)"

